data.description: ASSUMABLE 2.99% interest rate! Beat the 6%-7% current rate! Beautiful backyard entertaining space - covered patio AND entertaining patio. Living room AND Family room. Granite countertops in kitchen. This home has been lovingly cared for and is waiting for your family! Updated interior paint, newly stained fence, gas fireplace, 3 car garage (partitioned), dog wash station. The full bathroom across from the downstairs bedroom is perfect for a guest suite/teen room/MIL quarters. Wide side yards, large storage shed. A pre-listing inspection has been done for you and is available from your agent.
